WEBVTT

00:02.000 --> 00:04.440
RADIO PRESENTER: The time is 6.10.

00:04.440 --> 00:07.720
Barristers,
valiant public defenders,

00:07.720 --> 00:09.160
or a waste of taxpayers' money?

00:09.160 --> 00:11.080
The Government seems to
have taken a view.

00:11.080 --> 00:13.320
YOUTH: Try this one. Try this one.

00:13.320 --> 00:15.000
One critic accuses its legal
aid plans of

00:15.000 --> 00:17.960
"cutting justice for all as if
it were chips for dinner."

00:17.960 --> 00:21.600
That critic is Ashley Jeevaratnam,
barrister and blogger,
and he joins us now.

00:21.600 --> 00:23.080
Hey... You all right, fam?

00:23.080 --> 00:24.600
Mr Jeevaratnam, good morning.

00:24.600 --> 00:28.320
Good morning, Kirsty, yes, I blog
at the compassionatebarrister.com

00:28.320 --> 00:33.480
So, how should barristers be paid?
Well, this is a very serious matter.

00:33.480 --> 00:40.520
This programme
contains strong language.

00:42.000 --> 00:48.074
